events.title: General Custer dies at the Battle of Little Bighorn

movie.title: They Died with Their Boots On
movie.plot: The story follows General George Armstrong Custer's adventures from his West Point days to his death. He defies orders during the Civil War, trains the 7th Cavalry, appeases Chief Crazy Horse and later engages in bloody battle with the Sioux nation.

movie.title: Iron Jawed Angels
movie.plot: Defiant young activists take the women's suffrage movement by storm, putting their lives at risk to help American women win the right to vote.
movie.awards: Won 1 Golden Globe. Another 3 wins & 27 nominations.
